flowchart TD
    A([User visits homepage]) --> B{Library configured?}
    B -- No --> C[Display setup form]
    C --> D[User enters library name\nand browses for directory path]
    D --> E[Submit]
    E --> F[Scan library directory\nfor book files]
    F --> G[Extract metadata\nAuthor · Title · Format · etc.]
    G --> H[(Store in SQLite)]
    H --> I
    B -- Yes --> I[Display library]
    I --> J([Wait for user activity])
